🔹 kubnelet
•	Agent running on every node
•	Talks to API Server
•	Ensures containers are running as defined

🔹 Container Runtime
•	Actually runs containers
•	Examples:
o	containerd
o	CRI-O
o	(Docker via containerd)

🔹 kube-proxy
•	Handles networking
•	Enables:
o	Service → Pod communication
o	Load balancing via iptables/IPVS

