Summary of Workflow
User sends a command (via kubectl) to the API Server.
API Server records the intent in etcd.
Scheduler sees the new requirement, picks a Worker Node, and tells the API Server.
Kubelet on that specific worker node sees the assignment and instructs the Container Runtime to pull the image and start the container.
Kube-proxy ensures the network is updated so the new container can be reached

One-line Summary
Kubernetes = Control Plane decides, Worker Nodes execute, etcd remembers, kubelet enforces, and Services connect everything.
